column8: planet_threshold_desc:This was my strategy at first but I saw it wasnt worth my time for the return.
column10: dig_threshold_desc:At first this number was 10 then I moved it to around 25 but sometimes wanted to go past that just to make sure the numbers didnt jump up.
column12: surprise_desc:Some planets paid well and I would stay a little longer just to see
column14: dynamic_desc:If the number drastically dropped by half I wouldnt stay long.   If it slowly went down I tried to milk it.
column16: other_desc:At first I wanted every gem but new I was timed so tried to get the most out of it knowing that at first I went past 0 several times to see if it would eventually give me gems.
